@page "/"
<PageTitle>CoreKit</PageTitle>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Phase 13</p>
        <h1>CoreKit is running inside a tenant workspace.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            This host combines hosted auth, tenant resolution, tenant-aware persistence, and tenant-scoped user workflows across modules.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-card">
        <h2>Current focus</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Hosted login and logout through the server</li>
            <li>Tenant-aware persistence per request</li>
            <li>Unified RPC via <code>/api/rpc</code></li>
            <li>Tenant administration and first real Customers module slice</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="grid">
    <article class="panel">
        <h2>Authentication</h2>
        <AuthorizeView>
            <Authorized>
                <p>Signed in as <strong>@context.User.Identity?.Name</strong>.</p>
            </Authorized>
            <NotAuthorized>
                <p>Not signed in yet. Use the login page to test the hosted auth flow.</p>
            </NotAuthorized>
        </AuthorizeView>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
        <h2>Host context</h2>
        <p>This host is tenant-scoped and is where module UI, tenant data access, and tenant administration belong.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
        <h2>Next milestone</h2>
        <p>Expand business modules and tenant-scoped operations on top of the new tenant management baseline.</p>
    </article>
</section>
